{"tid":1434975,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"艾未未:共產黨宣佈對港強硬,只是虛張聲勢","createTime":"2019-08-09T02:21:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T02:44:51.000Z","uid":25345,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2587ff0014685404e7ab056327cd52402d120f97","tid":1434975,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:21:11.000Z","msg":"香港因「反送中」而起的抗議運動日益激烈，旅居德國的中國維權藝術家艾未未預言，類似六四事件的鎮壓有可能在香港發生，但中國會為此付出巨大代價。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【逆權運動】警總爆手足口病有警員正休假 網傳「忍屎忍尿」睡眠不足致病倒<br />\n<br />\n艾未未接受「德國之星」電台專訪，認為北京政府近日就香港示威的強硬表態只是「虛張聲勢」。他說：「幾十年來，他們都是這樣做的。中國國內的任何地方發生類似事件，他們都會動用坦克、軍隊或其他任何手段加以鎮壓。他們可以變得非常殘酷血腥。<span style=\"color: red;\">但這是在香港，他們其實是在虛張聲勢。情況遠遠超出他們的想像，而那些年輕人並沒有害怕。那是他們生存之戰。」</span>"},{"pid":"981638fc5188bf20c0279c41b6b9320c001e5042","tid":1434975,"uid":171450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:22:13.000Z","msg":"艾未未 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0217136c6de10334824d3a6077b1ff96622ee2e0","tid":1434975,"uid":289978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:28:27.000Z","msg":"一味靠嚇"},{"pid":"e71b5cab57e26c6f54dfb9a7bc28410c589e0489","tid":1434975,"uid":197640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:30:24.000Z","msg":"一出支軍，第七艦隊不遠了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5535798c18f36b899330837a83fa52a8976b13bc","tid":1434975,"uid":126305,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:34:14.000Z","msg":"生死存亡"},{"pid":"275dcef8aa15571e85b0809726bd1bb38482c3c1","tid":1434975,"uid":171718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:36:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee0a4be5fb6772a4d5521c9dd831d1564d5f4a99","tid":1434975,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score